WEBVTT

00:00:59.482 --> 00:01:02.489
she was just one minute
and 12 seconds too slow.

00:01:02.823 --> 00:01:07.410
(Clip) A bittersweet moment
as she finishes in fourth place.

00:01:07.434 --> 00:01:09.735
(Music)

00:01:09.759 --> 00:01:12.514
AG: Four years later,
she had another chance.

00:01:12.538 --> 00:01:14.537
It was 2016 in Los Angeles.

00:01:14.878 --> 00:01:16.989
After all that grueling training,

00:01:17.013 --> 00:01:20.728
Amy started out in the front of the pack
and stayed there for over an hour.

00:01:21.251 --> 00:01:23.561
But halfway through,
Amy started to struggle.

00:01:23.918 --> 00:01:27.258
AC: And there was one point
where I started kind of hurting,

00:01:27.282 --> 00:01:29.543
and I think I said,
"This feels a little spicy."

00:01:29.567 --> 00:01:31.766
It was just a little too much in my legs